---
title: Pumpkin Spice Chocolate Truffles Serves 2 | with Toasted Almonds
description: Sink your teeth into creamy, chocolatey heaven with these pumpkin spice chocolate truffles, rolled in a blend of toasted almonds and fragrant cocoa.  The ultimate post- dinner treat!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pumpkin-spice-chocolate-truffles-7f11ca7f-2066f598.jpg
